      <body>
         <div xml:id="main">
            <head type="incipit">
               <supplied reason="XTF-compatibility">Greetings to all to whom this present letter reaches ¶  ¶ Since the Academic grades were instituted by this Council, so that men who are pre-eminent in ability and learning may be decorated by distinc...</supplied>
            </head>
            <p rend="number" xml:lang="de">92.04.30</p>
            <p rend="correspondent" xml:lang="de">From McGill University</p>
            <p rend="location" xml:lang="de">RB MSS M200b.60, Library, Royal Botanic Gardens Melbourne.<seg rend="FootnoteReference" style=""/>
            </p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; text-align: center; "
               xml:lang="de">
               <note type="footnote" xml:id="_ftn0" n="1">
                  <p rend="FootnoteText"
                     style="margin-left: 0.3333in; text-indent: -0.3333in; font-size: 9pt; hyphenate: false; "
                     xml:lang="en">
                     <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>The certificate bears the seal of McGill University.</p>
                  <p rend="FootnoteText"
                     style="margin-left: 0.3333in; text-indent: -0.3333in; font-size: 9pt; hyphenate: false; "
                     xml:lang="en">
                     <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>A<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>giant<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
                     <seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="font-style: italic; ">Todea</seg>
                     <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>that M presented to the University is closely associated with this award. An article in the<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
                     <seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="font-style: italic; ">Australasian</seg>
                     <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>(27 August 1892, p.<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>394), reports that M 'had taken it upon himself to ship the plant on 25 March last'; M had estimated that it would weigh about one ton without fronds (D. Penhallow to W. Thiselton-Dyer, 22 April 1892, RBG Kew, Directors' correspondence, vol 195, f. 308). The<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
                     <seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="font-style: italic; ">Todea</seg>
                     <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>was in good growth in 1894<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>(D. Penhallow to D. Morris, 10 May 1894,<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>RBG Kew, Directors' correspondence, vol 195, f. 309).</p>
               </note>
               <seg rend="formtext"
                    style="font-weight: normal; font-style: normal; color: #0070C0; font-size: 12pt; ">Universitas McGill</seg>
            </p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; text-align: center; "
               xml:lang="de">
               <seg rend="formtext"
                    style="font-weight: normal; font-style: normal; color: #0070C0; font-size: 12pt; ">Monte Regio, in Provincia Canadensi.</seg>
            </p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; text-align: center; "
               xml:lang="de">
               <seg rend="formtext"
                    style="font-weight: normal; font-style: normal; color: #0070C0; font-size: 12pt; ">Omnibus ad quos hae Literae Praesentes Pervenerint, Salutem</seg>
               <seg rend="formtext"
                    style="font-weight: normal; font-style: normal; color: #0070C0; font-size: 12pt; ">.</seg>
            </p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="de">
               <seg rend="formtext"
                    style="font-weight: normal; font-style: normal; color: #0070C0; font-size: 12pt; ">Quum Gradus Academici hoc Consilio instituti fuerint, ut viri ingenio et doctrina praestantes insignibus honoris praeter ceteros ornarentur. Nos igitur Regentes, Primarius et Socii Collegii McGill virum doctissimum</seg>
               <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>Baronem Fredericum Von Mueller K.C.M.G., F.R.S.<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
               <seg rend="formtext"
                    style="font-weight: normal; font-style: normal; color: #0070C0; font-size: 12pt; ">N</seg>
               <seg rend="formtext"
                    style="font-weight: normal; font-style: normal; color: #0070C0; font-size: 12pt; ">e</seg>
               <seg rend="formtext"
                    style="font-weight: normal; font-style: normal; color: #0070C0; font-size: 12pt; ">
                  <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>honore bene merito</seg>
               <seg rend="formtext"
                    style="font-weight: normal; font-style: normal; color: #0070C0; font-size: 12pt; ">
                  <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>careat</seg>
               <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>Doctorem in utroque jure<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
               <seg rend="formtext"
                    style="font-weight: normal; font-style: normal; color: #0070C0; font-size: 12pt; ">Honoris causa renunciavimus et constituimus</seg>
            </p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="de">
               <seg rend="formtext"
                    style="font-weight: normal; font-style: normal; color: #0070C0; font-size: 12pt; ">In cujus rei Testimonium Sigillum Universitatis Literis hisce rite subscriptis apponi fecimus.</seg>
            </p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="de">
               <seg rend="formtext"
                    style="font-weight: normal; font-style: normal; color: #0070C0; font-size: 12pt; ">Datae in Comitiis solennibus<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
               </seg>
               <seg rend="formtext"
                    style="font-weight: normal; font-style: normal; color: #0070C0; font-size: 12pt; ">die,<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
               </seg>tricesima<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>Mensis Aprilis<seg rend="formtext"
                    style="font-weight: normal; font-style: normal; color: #0070C0; font-size: 12pt; ">, Anno Domini, MDCCCXCII</seg>
            </p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-size: 12pt; margin-left: 1.75in; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="de">Donaldus A Smith K.C.M.G. LLD. Cancellarius</p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-size: 12pt; margin-left: 1.75in; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="de">J. Gulielmus Dawson, LLD, Primarius.</p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-size: 12pt; margin-left: 1.75in; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="de">Georgius Cornish, LL.D., Socius.</p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-size: 12pt; margin-left: 1.75in; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="de">Jacobus W Brakenridge BCL. Protabularius</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 10pt; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">Greetings to all to whom this present letter reaches</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 10pt; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Since the Academic grades were instituted by this Council, so that men who are pre-eminent in ability and learning may be decorated by distinctions of honour beyond others, we therefore, the Regents, Principal and Fellows of McGill College have declared and appointed the most learned man Baron Frederick von Mueller<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>K.C.M.G., F.R.S.<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>as Doctor<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
               <seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="font-style: italic; ">Honoris causa</seg>
               <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>in<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>each<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>law<seg rend="FootnoteReference" style="">
                  <note type="footnote" xml:id="_ftn1" n="2">
                     <p rend="FootnoteText"
                        style="margin-left: 0.3333in; text-indent: -0.3333in; font-size: 9pt; hyphenate: false; "
                        xml:lang="en">
                        <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>i.e. canon law and civil law.</p>
                  </note>
               </seg>
               <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>lest he lack<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>the<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>well-deserved honour. As testimony of this matter we have had the seal of the University placed properly at the bottom of this letter.</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 10pt; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Given at the solemn assembly on the thirtieth day of the month of April in the year of the Lord 1892.</p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="margin-left: 1.75in; font-size: 10pt; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">Donald A Smith K.C.M.G. LLD. Chancellor</p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="margin-left: 1.75in; font-size: 10pt; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">J.<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>William<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>Dawson, LLD, Principal.</p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="margin-left: 1.75in; font-size: 10pt; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">George<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>Cornish, LL.D., Fellow.</p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="margin-left: 1.75in; font-size: 10pt; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">James<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>W Brakenridge BCL. Pro Registrar</p>
         </div>
      </body>
